OL,3,CWhat options are available to Court of
OL,4,CAppeal in the Valdo Calocane case?
OL,6,FThe complex arrangements are
OL,7,Fessentially a direction for treatment
OL,8,Frather than seen as a penal punishment
OL,9,Fand, as such, it is not clear at this
OL,10,Fstage how judges could increase the
OL,11,Fsentence to make it more stringent.
OL,13,FJudge Mr Justice Turner made a
OL,14,Fhospital order for Calocane to be
OL,15,Freadmitted and detained at Ashworth
OL,16,FHigh Security Hospital, near
OL,17,FLiverpool, under sections 37 and 41 of
OL,18,Fthe Mental Health Act 1983.
