OL,3,CWhat options are available to Court of
OL,4,CAppeal in the Valdo Calocane case?
OL,6,FIt means Calocane will be detained in
OL,7,Fa psychiatric hospital for treatment
OL,8,Fand will not be discharged until he is
OL,9,Fdeemed well enough and either the
OL,10,FJustice Secretary or a Mental Health
OL,11,FTribunal assess that he no longer
OL,12,Fposes a risk to the public.
OL,14,FDuring sentencing, the judge said he
OL,15,Fwas "entirely satisfied on the
OL,16,Fevidence, in the particular
OL,17,Fcircumstances of this case and for the
OL,18,Freasons I have given" that this was
OL,19,Fthe "proper sentence" to impose.
