OL,6,FThe Attorney General's considerations
OL,7,Fdid not look at whether the correct
OL,8,Fcharge was pursued in Calocane's case,
OL,9,Fthe Press Association news agency
OL,10,Funderstands.
OL,12,FAnother sentencing option is to
OL,13,Freconsider whether it is appropriate
