OL,6,FBut, during sentencing, Judge Mr
OL,7,FJustice Turner set out his reasons as
OL,8,Fto why a 45A hospital order ` known as
OL,9,Fa hybrid order as it imposes a prison
OL,10,Fsentence and directs admission to
OL,11,Fhospital ` would not be appropriate.
